<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.9">
<l>veṭpuḻuti mēṟpeytukoṇ ṭaḷaintatōr vēḻattiṟ karuṅkaṉṟupōl</l>
<l>teṭpuḻuti yāṭittiri vikkiramaṟ ciṟupukar paṭaviyarttu</l>
<l>oṭpōta larkama lacciṟukkā luṟaittoṉṟu nōvāmē</l>
<l>taṭpōtu koṇṭatavi ciṉmītē taḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the one dark elephant calf that wallowed,</l>
<l>having poured white dust upon [himself],</l>
<l>Trivikrama, having played in fine dust,</l>
<l>sweats so that small spots appear,</l>
<l>[his] small lotus feet with bright flower buds</l>
<l>fall without once feeling pain,</l>
<l>will he come onto the cushion with cool buds with a tottering walk?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
